                            <comment id="472504" author="adilger" created="Tue, 23 Sep 2025 08:12:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Together with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/61412&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/61412&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16738&quot; title=&quot;Improve mount.lustre with many MGS NIDs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16738&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16738&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; utils: add mgsname mount option for custom hostname display&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;) to preserve the MGS hostname in the &lt;tt&gt;/proc/mounts&lt;/tt&gt; output, it will remain possible to use the output from &lt;tt&gt;mount&lt;/tt&gt; to generate a new mount command-line without showing dozens of MGS NIDs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
